#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#. newlines at the end are deliberate, and function as spacers before the [option]s
#: data/internal/resources/AMLAs/_main.cfg:357
msgid ""
"Congratulations, your $unit.language_name has leveled up... but theyâre "
"already at their max level!\n"
"\n"
"When this happens, <span color='#0D87B6'><b>some campaigns</b></span> â like "
"this one â allow you to select a minor bonus to hitpoints or damage. These "
"bonuses are called âAMLAsâ: âAfter Maximum Level Advancementsâ. If your max-"
"level units have normal, <span color='#0D87B6'><b>blue experience bars</b></"
"span>, that means these AMLAs are available.\n"
"\n"
"<span color='#9608CF'><b><i>Other campaigns</i></b></span> donât have these "
"AMLA options, and instead always give max-level units +3 max hp when they "
"level up. If your max-level units have <span color='#9608CF'><b>purple "
"experience bars</b></span>, theyâll only get +3 max hp when they level up.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"GratulĂĄlunk, a $unit.language_name egysĂŠg szintet lĂŠpett... ĂĄmde mĂĄr "
"jelenleg is a maximĂĄlis szintjĂźkĂśn vannak!\n"
"\n"
"Amikor ez megtĂśrtĂŠnik, <span color='#0D87B6'><b>egyes hadjĂĄratok</b></span> "
"â pĂŠldĂĄul ez â lehetĹvĂŠ teszik, hogy egy kisebb bĂłnuszt vĂĄlassz az "
"ĂŠleterĹpontokhoz vagy a sebzĂŠshez. Ezeket a bĂłnuszokat \"LSzUSz-"
"nak\" (LegfelsĹbb Szint UtĂĄni SzintlĂŠpĂŠs) nevezik. Ha a maximĂĄlis szintĹą "
"egysĂŠgek normĂĄl, <span color='#0D87B6'><b>kĂŠk ĂŠlmĂŠnysĂĄvokkal</b></span> "
"rendelkeznek, az azt jelenti, hogy ezek az LSzUSz-ok elĂŠrhetĹk.\n"
"\n"
"<span color='#9608CF'><b><i>MĂĄs hadjĂĄratok</i></b></span> nem rendelkeznek "
"ezekkel az LSzUSz opciĂłkkal, ehelyett mindig +3 maximĂĄlis ĂŠleterĹt adnak a "
"maximĂĄlis szintĹą egysĂŠgeknek, amikor szintet lĂŠpnek. Ha a maximĂĄlis szintĹą "
"egysĂŠgeid <span color='#9608CF'><b>lila tapasztalati sĂĄvokkal</b></span> "
"rendelkeznek, akkor csak +3 maximĂĄlis ĂŠleterĹt kapnak, ha szintet lĂŠpnek.\n"

