#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:4
msgid ""
"Use the map editorâs <i>Areas</i> menu to define regions later addressed by "
"event or AI coding."
msgstr ""
"HasznĂĄld a tĂŠrkĂŠpszerkesztĹ <i>TerĂźletek</i> menĂźpontjĂĄt azon tĂŠrkĂŠprĂŠszek "
"kijelĂślĂŠsĂŠre, melyekre kĂŠsĹbb esemĂŠny vagy MI kĂłdolĂĄs hivatkozik."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:5 data/tips.cfg:9 data/tips.cfg:13
msgid "<i>â The Wesnoth Design Guide</i>"
msgstr "<i>â Wesnoth taktikai ĂştmutatĂł</i>"

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:8
msgid ""
"In the map editor, select <i>New Scenario</i> in the <i>File</i> menu to "
"make use of advanced features."
msgstr ""
"HasznĂĄld az <i>Ăj kĂźldetĂŠs</i> lehetĹsĂŠget a tĂŠrkĂŠpszerkesztĹ <i>FĂĄjl</i> "
"menĂźpontjĂĄban a haladĂł beĂĄllĂ­tĂĄsok kihasznĂĄlĂĄsa ĂŠrdekĂŠben."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:12
msgid ""
"Scenarios saved from the editor in their default folder can be selected in "
"the <i>Custom Scenarios</i> section of the Multiplayer âCreate Gameâ screen."
msgstr ""
"A tĂŠrkĂŠpszerkesztĹbĹl az alapĂŠrtelmezett mappĂĄba mentett kĂźldetĂŠsek a "
"<i>FelhasznĂĄlĂłi kĂźldetĂŠsek</i> menĂźponton keresztĂźl kivĂĄlaszthatĂłak a "
"tĂśbbjĂĄtĂŠkos \"JĂĄtĂŠk lĂŠtrehozĂĄsa\" kĂŠpernyĹjĂŠn."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:16
msgid ""
"Donât neglect to earn your leader experience! You need to keep him safe, but "
"if you coddle him too much he may be too weak to survive future battles."
msgstr ""
"Ăgyelj rĂĄ, hogy a vezĂŠred is szerezzen tapasztalatot! Ugyan vigyĂĄznod kell "
"rĂĄ, de ha tĂşlsĂĄgosan elkĂŠnyezteted, akkor nagyon gyenge lesz ahhoz, hogy "
"tĂşlĂŠlje az elkĂśvetkezendĹ csatĂĄkat."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:17
msgid "<i>â Great Mage Delfador, 520YW</i>"
msgstr "<i>â Delfador nagymĂĄgus, W.i.sz. 520</i>"

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:20
msgid ""
"In the <b>Actions</b> menu, you can select <b>Show Enemy Moves</b> to "
"highlight all the hexes your adversary can move to (assuming your units stay "
"where they are). Use this to make sure the enemy canât reach your weak or "
"injured units on his next turn."
msgstr ""
"A <b>Parancsok</b> menĂźben vĂĄlaszd az <b>EllensĂŠges lĂŠpĂŠsek mutatĂĄsa</b> "
"pontot, ha lĂĄtni szeretnĂŠd az Ăśsszes lehetsĂŠges mezĹt, ahovĂĄ az ellensĂŠged "
"lĂŠphet (feltĂŠtelezve, hogy egysĂŠgeid ott maradnak, ahol vannak). Ezzel "
"megbizonyosodhatsz arrĂłl, hogy a kĂśvetkezĹ kĂśrben az ellensĂŠg nem ĂŠrheti el "
"a te gyenge vagy sĂŠrĂźlt egysĂŠgeidet."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:21 data/tips.cfg:33 data/tips.cfg:37 data/tips.cfg:45
#: data/tips.cfg:49 data/tips.cfg:65 data/tips.cfg:69 data/tips.cfg:73
#: data/tips.cfg:77 data/tips.cfg:81 data/tips.cfg:93 data/tips.cfg:97
#: data/tips.cfg:101 data/tips.cfg:113 data/tips.cfg:121 data/tips.cfg:125
#: data/tips.cfg:133 data/tips.cfg:161 data/tips.cfg:165 data/tips.cfg:173
#: data/tips.cfg:181 data/tips.cfg:189 data/tips.cfg:198 data/tips.cfg:202
#: data/tips.cfg:206 data/tips.cfg:214 data/tips.cfg:234 data/tips.cfg:242
#: data/tips.cfg:250 data/tips.cfg:266 data/tips.cfg:271 data/tips.cfg:276
#: data/tips.cfg:282
msgid "<i>â The Wesnoth Tactical Guide</i>"
msgstr "<i>â Wesnoth taktikai ĂştmutatĂł</i>"

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:24
msgid ""
"Units with the <i>Intelligent</i> trait need fewer experience points to "
"level up. Early in a campaign, try to give killing blows to these units so "
"you can get some high-level troops sooner."
msgstr ""
"Az <i>eszes</i> jellemvonĂĄssal rendelkezĹ egysĂŠgeknek kevesebb tapasztalati "
"pontra van szĂźksĂŠgĂźk ahhoz, hogy szintet lĂŠpjenek. A hadjĂĄratok elejĂŠn "
"prĂłbĂĄlj Ăşgy taktikĂĄzni, hogy ezek az egysĂŠgek adjĂĄk le a halĂĄlos csapĂĄsokat, "
"Ă­gy hamarabb lesznek magasabb szintĹą egysĂŠgeid."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:25
msgid "<i>â King Konrad, 536YW</i>"
msgstr "<i>â Konrad kirĂĄly, w.i.sz. 536.</i>"

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:28
msgid ""
"The encircling tactic is very powerful, particularly against fast opponents. "
"By placing two units on opposite sides of an enemy, their zones of control "
"will restrict it to one hex of movement in any direction. Unfortunately, you "
"must completely surround skirmishers to immobilize them."
msgstr ""
"A kĂśrbekerĂ­tĂŠs taktikĂĄja nagyon hatĂĄsos, kĂźlĂśnĂśsen a gyors ellenfelek "
"esetĂŠn. Helyezz egy-egy egysĂŠget az ellenfĂŠl kĂŠt szemkĂśzti oldalĂĄra, Ă­gy az "
"ellenĹrzĂśtt terĂźleteik megakadĂĄlyozzĂĄk, hogy az ellenfĂŠl egynĂŠl tĂśbb mezĹt "
"lĂŠphessen bĂĄrmilyen irĂĄnyba. A portyĂĄzĂł egysĂŠgeket sajnos teljesen kĂśrbe "
"kell venni, kĂźlĂśnben szabadon mozoghatnak."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:29 data/tips.cfg:141
msgid "<i>â Memoirs of Gweddry, 627YW</i>"
msgstr "<i>â Gweddry emlĂŠkiratai, w.i.sz. 627.</i>"

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:32
msgid ""
"You can access the <b>Recruit</b> and <b>Recall</b> commands by right-"
"clicking on a castle tile. That will let you choose the precise hex you put "
"a unit in. Placing units wisely can sometimes let you reach a village a turn "
"earlier."
msgstr ""
"A <b>ToborzĂĄs</b> ĂŠs <b>VisszahĂ­vĂĄs</b> parancsokat hĂ­vd elĹ Ăşgy, hogy jobb "
"gombbal a vĂĄr valamelyik mezĹjĂŠre kattintasz. Ăgy te dĂśntheted el, hogy az "
"egysĂŠg melyik mezĹre kerĂźljĂśn. Ha bĂślcsen helyezed el az egysĂŠgeidet, az "
"nĂŠha azt jelentheti, hogy egy kĂśrrel hamarabb ĂŠrsz el egy falut."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:36
msgid ""
"There are some helpful summary screens in the main menu: for instance, the "
"<b>Status Table</b> will let you know how your enemies are doing, and how "
"you are doing in comparison."
msgstr ""
"A fĹmenĂźbĹl elĂŠrhetĹ nĂŠhĂĄny ĂĄttekintĹ tĂĄblĂĄzat, amelyek nagy segĂ­tsĂŠget "
"jelenthetnek: pĂŠldĂĄul a <b>Csapatok adatai</b> megmutatja, hogy az "
"ellenfeleid, illetve hozzĂĄjuk kĂŠpest te, hogy ĂĄlltok."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:40
msgid ""
"Units with the <i>Quick</i> trait get an extra movement point per turn. This "
"can be very important when moving through difficult terrain such as water or "
"caves. It can make the difference between being able to move one hex or two."
msgstr ""
"A <i>gyors</i> jellemvonĂĄssal rendelkezĹ egysĂŠgek egy mezĹvel tĂśbbet "
"lĂŠphetnek minden kĂśrben. Ez fĹleg akkor szĂĄmĂ­that sokat, amikor az egysĂŠgnek "
"nehĂŠz terepen kell ĂĄtkelnie, mint pĂŠldĂĄul vĂ­z vagy barlang. Ilyenkor ez a "
"kĂźlĂśnbsĂŠg azt jelentheti, hogy az egysĂŠg egy kĂśr alatt egy vagy kĂŠt mezĹt "
"tud-e mozogni."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:41 data/tips.cfg:117 data/tips.cfg:218 data/tips.cfg:230
msgid "<i>â High Lord Kalenz, 470YW</i>"
msgstr "<i>â Kalenz fĹlord, w.i.sz. 470.</i>"

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:44
msgid ""
"After you have played a few scenarios, read the <b>Gameplay</b> section in "
"the <b>Help</b> screen carefully. Details become important as scenarios get "
"harder!"
msgstr ""
"MiutĂĄn lejĂĄtszottĂĄl mĂĄr nĂŠhĂĄny kĂźldetĂŠst, olvasd el figyelmesen a "
"<b>JĂĄtĂŠkmenet</b> fejezetet a sĂşgĂłban. Ahogy a kĂźldetĂŠsek nehezednek, a "
"rĂŠszletek egyre fontosabbĂĄ vĂĄlnak!"

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:48
msgid ""
"It is usually better to start the next scenario in a campaign with lower-"
"level units that are about to level up than with those same units at a "
"higher level."
msgstr ""
"ĂltalĂĄban jobb egy hadjĂĄrat kĂśvetkezĹ kĂźldetĂŠsĂŠt alacsonyabb szintĹą "
"egysĂŠgekkel kezdeni, melyek kĂśzel vannak a szintlĂŠpĂŠshez, mint az azonos "
"tĂ­pusĂş, de magasabb szintĹą egysĂŠgekkel."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:52
msgid ""
"On www.wesnoth.org you can find strategy guides, technical support, the "
"history of Wesnoth, and much more."
msgstr ""
"A www.wesnoth.org honlapon talĂĄlhatsz stratĂŠgiai ĂştmutatĂłkat, technikai "
"segĂ­tsĂŠget, Ă­rĂĄsokat Wesnoth tĂśrtĂŠnetĂŠrĹl ĂŠs mĂŠg sok egyebet."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:53
msgid "<i>â The Wesnoth Community</i>"
msgstr "<i>â A Wesnoth KĂśzĂśssĂŠg</i>"

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:56
msgid ""
"<i>Lawful</i> units fight better by day, and <i>chaotic</i> units fight "
"better at night. <i>Neutral</i> units are unaffected by the time of day. The "
"rare <i>liminal</i> units fight best during twilight."
msgstr ""
"Az <i>igazsĂĄgos</i> egysĂŠgek nappal, a <i>tĂśrvĂŠnytelen</i> egysĂŠgek ĂŠjszaka "
"harcolnak jobban. A <i>semleges</i> egysĂŠgeket nem ĂŠrinti a napszakok "
"vĂĄltozĂĄsa. A ritka <i>ingatag</i> egysĂŠgek szĂźrkĂźletkor vannak erejĂźk "
"teljĂŠben."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:57
msgid ""
"<i>â Royal Compendium of Battle Terminology: Volume II (reprinted 221YW)</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>â KirĂĄlyi vezĂŠrfonal a harcĂĄszati szaknyelvhez â II. kĂśtet, Ăşjranyomva w."
"i.sz. 221-ben</i>"

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:60
msgid ""
"An otherwise sound plan can fail if you attack at the wrong time of day."
msgstr ""
"Egy egyĂŠbkĂŠnt jĂłl hangzĂł terv is megbukhat, ha nem a megfelelĹ napszakban "
"tĂĄmadsz."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:61 data/tips.cfg:85 data/tips.cfg:137 data/tips.cfg:145
#: data/tips.cfg:222
msgid "<i>â Haldric II, 42YW, Handbook of Tactical Analysis: Volume I</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>â A taktikai analĂ­zis kĂŠzikĂśnyve, I. rĂŠsz â II. Haldric, w.i.sz. 42.</i>"

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:64
msgid ""
"If you are playing with <b>Shroud</b> or <b>Fog of War</b> active, you wonât "
"know what youâre facing. In this case, long-range scouting units are worth "
"their cost. Try to choose scouts that can easily move across the surrounding "
"terrain, because usually units can only see as far as they can move in one "
"turn."
msgstr ""
"Ha aktĂ­v <b>eltakarĂĄssal</b> vagy <b>kĂśddel</b> jĂĄtszol, akkor nem fogod "
"tudni, mivel ĂĄllsz szemben. Ebben az esetben a nagy hatĂłtĂĄvolsĂĄgĂş felderĂ­tĹ "
"egysĂŠgek jĂłcskĂĄn megĂŠrik az ĂĄrukat. VĂĄlassz olyan felderĂ­tĹket, amelyek "
"kĂśnnyen mozognak a kĂśrnyezĹ terepen, mert az egysĂŠgek csak addig lĂĄtnak el, "
"ameddig el is tudnĂĄnak jutni egy kĂśr alatt."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:68
msgid ""
"There are six types of attack: <i>pierce</i>, <i>blade</i>, <i>impact</i>, "
"<i>fire</i>, <i>cold</i> and <i>arcane</i>. Different units have weaknesses "
"against different types of attacks. Right-click on a unit and select <b>Unit "
"Type Description</b> to see which attacks it is resistant to, and which will "
"affect it the most."
msgstr ""
"HatfĂŠle tĂĄmadĂĄs lĂŠtezik: <i>szĂşrĂĄs</i>, <i>vĂĄgĂĄs</i>, <i>ĂźtĂŠs</i>, <i>tĹąz</"
"i>, <i>hideg</i> ĂŠs <i>fĂśldĂśntĂşli</i>. A kĂźlĂśnbĂśzĹ egysĂŠgek az egyes "
"tĂĄmadĂĄsokra kĂźlĂśnbĂśzĹ mĂŠrtĂŠkben ĂŠrzĂŠkenyek. Kattints a jobb gombbal egy "
"egysĂŠgre, ĂŠs vĂĄlaszd ki az <b>EgysĂŠg leĂ­rĂĄsa</b> pontot, hogy lĂĄsd, mely "
"tĂĄmadĂĄsokkal szemben ellenĂĄllĂł, ĂŠs melyek sebzik leginkĂĄbb."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:72
msgid ""
"The terrain occupied by your units is the main factor determining the chance "
"that they will be hit. The defensive rating for the currently selected unit "
"in the currently selected terrain is displayed in the top right corner of "
"the screen."
msgstr ""
"A terĂźlet fajtĂĄja hatĂĄrozza meg leginkĂĄbb, hogy a rajta ĂĄllĂł egysĂŠgeidet "
"milyen valĂłszĂ­nĹąsĂŠggel fogjĂĄk megĂźtni egy csatĂĄban. Az ĂŠppen kijelĂślt "
"egysĂŠgnek az egĂŠrmutatĂł alatti terĂźletfajtĂĄra vonatkozĂł vĂŠdekezĂŠsi ĂŠrtĂŠke a "
"kĂŠpernyĹ jobb felsĹ sarkĂĄban jelenik meg."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:76
msgid ""
"Poisoned units will lose eight hitpoints every turn until they are one point "
"from dying. They will then remain at deathâs door until the poison is "
"removed. Healers can prevent a poisoned unit from deteriorating, but the "
"poison will not be removed unless the unit regenerates, or begins a turn in "
"a village, in an oasis, or next to a unit with the <i>Cures</i> ability."
msgstr ""
"A megmĂŠrgezett egysĂŠgek nyolc ĂŠletpontot veszĂ­tenek minden kĂśrben, amĂ­g mĂĄr "
"csak egy pontjuk marad. Mindaddig a halĂĄl kapujĂĄban ĂĄllnak, amĂ­g a mĂŠreg "
"hat. A gyĂłgyĂ­tĂłk ĂştjĂĄt ĂĄllhatjĂĄk a tovĂĄbbi rosszabbodĂĄsnak, de a "
"mĂŠrgezettsĂŠg csak akkor mĂşlik el, ha az egysĂŠg regenerĂĄlĂłdik, illetve eltĂślt "
"egy kĂśrt egy faluban, vagy egy <i>gyĂłgyĂ­tĂĄs</i> kĂŠpessĂŠggel rendelkezĹ "
"egysĂŠg mellett."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:80
msgid ""
"You can reuse units from a previous scenario by selecting <b>Recall</b> from "
"the <b>Actions</b> menu. By recalling the same units over and over, you can "
"build up a powerful and experienced army."
msgstr ""
"Az elĹzĹ pĂĄlya egysĂŠgeit is Ăşjra csatasorba ĂĄllĂ­thatod a <b>Parancsok</b> "
"menĂź <b>VisszahĂ­vĂĄs</b> parancsĂĄval. Ha Ăşjra meg Ăşjra visszahĂ­vod "
"ugyanazokat az egysĂŠgeket, ĂźtĹkĂŠpes ĂŠs tapasztalt hadsereget tudsz "
"felĂŠpĂ­teni."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:84
msgid ""
"Units of level one and higher have a <i>Zone of Control</i> in the six hexes "
"around them. If a unit moves into an enemyâs zone of control, it may not "
"move any further that turn. This means that units can have two empty hexes "
"between them and still create a barrier to the enemy. Beware, though: "
"skirmishers can pass through these gaps."
msgstr ""
"A legalĂĄbb 1-es szintĹą egysĂŠgeknek van egy <i>ellenĹrzĂśtt terĂźlete</i> a "
"vele szomszĂŠdos hatszĂśgeken. Ha egy egysĂŠg az ellensĂŠg ellenĹrzĂśtt "
"terĂźletĂŠre lĂŠp, akkor abban a kĂśrben mĂĄr nem mehet tovĂĄbb. Ez azt jelenti, "
"hogy az egysĂŠgek mĂŠg Ăşgy is gĂĄtat szabhatnak az ellensĂŠg elĹrenyomulĂĄsĂĄnak, "
"ha kĂśzĂśttĂźk kĂŠt Ăźres mezĹ van. Ugyanakkor a portyĂĄzĂł egysĂŠgek mozgĂĄsuk sorĂĄn "
"figyelmen kĂ­vĂźl tudjĂĄk hagyjĂĄk ezeket a korlĂĄtokat."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:88
msgid ""
"The chance to hit a unit usually depends on how well that unit can defend "
"itself in the terrain in which it is standing. However, magical attacks "
"always have a 70% chance to hit, and units with the <i>Marksman</i> ability "
"are guaranteed at least a 60% chance of a hit when they attack on their own "
"turn."
msgstr ""
"Egy egysĂŠg sebezhetĹsĂŠge ĂĄltalĂĄban attĂłl fĂźgg, hogy az adott egysĂŠg milyen "
"jĂłl tudja megvĂŠdeni magĂĄt azon a terĂźleten, amelyen ĂŠppen ĂĄll, azonban a "
"mĂĄgikus tĂĄmadĂĄsok vĂŠdekezĂŠskor ĂŠs tĂĄmadĂĄskor is mindig 70% esĂŠllyel "
"talĂĄlnak, valamint a <i>mesterlĂśvĂŠszeknek</i> legalĂĄbb 60% esĂŠlyĂźk van a "
"sikeres lĂśvĂŠsre tĂĄmadĂĄskor."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:89
msgid "<i>â Haldric II, 43YW, Handbook of Tactical Analysis: Volume II</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>â A taktikai analĂ­zis kĂŠzikĂśnyve, I. rĂŠsz â II. Haldric, w.i.sz. 43.</i>"

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:92
msgid ""
"Units stationed in villages will either heal eight hitpoints at the "
"beginning of their turn, or will recover from poisoning."
msgstr ""
"A falvakban elhelyezett egysĂŠgek a kĂśvetkezĹ kĂśr elejĂŠn 8 ĂŠleterĹpontot (ĂP) "
"gyĂłgyulnak, vagy pedig felĂŠpĂźlnek a mĂŠrgezĂŠsbĹl."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:96
msgid ""
"Donât move an injured unit if you donât have to â let it rest. If a unit "
"does not move or attack, it will recover two hitpoints at the beginning of "
"its next turn."
msgstr ""
"Ne mozgasd sĂŠrĂźlt egysĂŠgeidet, hacsak nem muszĂĄj â hadd pihenjenek. Ha egy "
"egysĂŠg nem tĂĄmad ĂŠs nem is mozog egy kĂśrben, akkor a kĂśvetkezĹ kĂśr elejĂŠn 2 "
"ĂŠleterĹpontot (ĂP) gyĂłgyul."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:100
msgid ""
"On maps where <i>Shroud</i> or <i>Fog of War</i> has been enabled, all "
"unitsâ sightlines are limited by their maximum movement. If you have some "
"valuable but slow units, keep at least one fast unit with them so that you "
"are not caught out by a surprise attack."
msgstr ""
"Azokon a pĂĄlyĂĄkon, ahol az <i>eltakarĂĄs</i> vagy a <i>kĂśd</i> be van "
"kapcsolva, egy egysĂŠg lĂĄtĂłterĂŠt a mozgĂĄsi lehetĹsĂŠgei hatĂĄrozzĂĄk meg. Ha van "
"nĂŠhĂĄny ĂŠrtĂŠkes, de lassĂş egysĂŠged, mindig tarts mellettĂźk legalĂĄbb egy gyors "
"egysĂŠget, nehogy vĂĄratlan tĂĄmadĂĄs ĂŠrjen."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:104
msgid ""
"Foot units tend to defend better in villages and castles than in other "
"terrain types, while most mounted units do not gain any defensive advantages "
"from villages or castles."
msgstr ""
"A gyalogos egysĂŠgek jobban tudnak vĂŠdekezni a falvakban ĂŠs a vĂĄrakban, mint "
"bĂĄrmely mĂĄs terepen, ugyanakkor ezeken a terĂźleteken a legtĂśbb lovas egysĂŠg "
"nem jut semmilyen elĹnyhĂśz."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:105 data/tips.cfg:185
msgid "<i>â Sir Kaylan, 498YW</i>"
msgstr "<i>â Sir Kaylan, w.i.sz. 498.</i>"

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:108
msgid ""
"Horse-based units are generally resistant to attacks with bladed or impact "
"weapons, but are vulnerable to attacks with piercing weapons, including bows "
"and spears."
msgstr ""
"A lovas egysĂŠgek ellenĂĄllnak a vĂĄgĂł ĂŠs ĂźtĹ fegyvereknek, de sebezhetĹek "
"szĂşrĂłfegyverekkel, tĂśbbek kĂśzt nyilakkal ĂŠs lĂĄndzsĂĄkkal."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:109
msgid "<i>â Sir Kaylan, 502YW</i>"
msgstr "<i>â Sir Kaylan, w.i.sz. 502.</i>"

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:112
msgid ""
"Inflicting the killing blow on an enemy unit is the best way to gain "
"experience. Units killing an enemy will gain eight experience points for "
"every level of the unit they kill, or four experience points for a zero-"
"level opponent."
msgstr ""
"A legjobb mĂłdja a tapasztalatszerzĂŠsnek, ha halĂĄlos ĂźtĂŠst mĂŠrĂźnk egy "
"ellensĂŠges egysĂŠgre. Azok az egysĂŠgek, amelyek megĂślnek valakit, 8 "
"tapasztalati pontot (TP) nyernek a legyĹzĂśtt ellensĂŠges egysĂŠg minden "
"szintje utĂĄn, illetve a 0. szintĹą egysĂŠgek utĂĄn 4-et."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:116
msgid ""
"Elvish units move and fight well in forest. Dwarvish units move and fight "
"well in hills, mountains and caves."
msgstr ""
"A tĂźnde egysĂŠgek kivĂĄlĂłan mozognak ĂŠs harcolnak erdĹkben. A tĂśrpĂśk legjobb "
"tudĂĄsukat dombokon, hegysĂŠgekben ĂŠs barlangokban mutatjĂĄk meg."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:120
msgid ""
"Patience is often key. Rather than attacking in bad conditions or with few "
"troops, wait for better conditions and then attack."
msgstr ""
"A tĂźrelem gyakran valĂłban rĂłzsĂĄt terem. InkĂĄbb vĂĄrj, amĂ­g jobb kĂśrĂźlmĂŠnyek "
"lesznek a tĂĄmadĂĄsra, minthogy rossz helyzetbĹl vagy kevĂŠs egysĂŠggel "
"bocsĂĄtkozz csatĂĄba."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:124
msgid ""
"If you are attacked from several directions, it may be a good idea to send "
"expendable units in some directions to delay enemy units."
msgstr ""
"Ha tĂśbb irĂĄnybĂłl tĂĄmadnak rĂĄd, jĂł Ăśtlet lehet nĂŠhĂĄny felĂĄldozhatĂł egysĂŠg "
"elĹrekĂźldĂŠse kĂźlĂśnbĂśzĹ irĂĄnyokba, hogy feltartsĂĄk az ellensĂŠget."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:128
msgid ""
"Do not be afraid to retreat and regroup; it is often the key to victory."
msgstr ""
"Ne fĂŠlj visszavonulni ĂŠs rendezni soraid, gyakran ez a gyĹzelem kulcsa."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:129
msgid "<i>â Meneldur, 123YW</i>"
msgstr "<i>â Meneldur, w.i.sz. 123.</i>"

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:132
msgid ""
"In most campaigns you will receive a gold bonus for finishing early, "
"depending on the number of villages on the map and the number of turns "
"remaining. You will usually earn more gold this way than through capturing "
"villages and waiting for the turns to run out."
msgstr ""
"A legtĂśbb hadjĂĄratban â a pĂĄlyĂĄn talĂĄlhatĂł falvak ĂŠs a kihasznĂĄlatlan kĂśrĂśk "
"szĂĄmĂĄtĂłl fĂźggĹen â tĂśbbletarannyal jutalmazzĂĄk a gyors befejezĂŠst. ĂltalĂĄban "
"tĂśbb aranyat nyersz ilyen mĂłdon, mintha a hĂĄtralevĹ kĂśrĂśket falvak "
"elfoglalĂĄsĂĄra hasznĂĄlnĂĄd."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:136
msgid ""
"<i>Leaders</i> can recruit or recall units from any keep inside a castle, "
"not just the keep they start on. Sometimes your allies may be willing to "
"make room for you on their keep so you can recruit from there, and you can "
"even capture an enemyâs keep and use that."
msgstr ""
"A <i>vezĂŠred</i> egy vĂĄr bĂĄrmely vĂĄrtornyĂĄbĂłl tud egysĂŠget toborozni vagy "
"visszahĂ­vni, nem csak onnan, ahol a jĂĄtĂŠkot kezdte. Elfoglalhatod az "
"ellensĂŠg vĂĄrtornyĂĄt is, ĂŠs toborozhatsz onnan, vagy a szĂśvetsĂŠgeseid is "
"tarthatnak fent neked helyet a vĂĄrukban, hogy ott vegyĂŠl fel Ăşj egysĂŠgeket."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:140
msgid ""
"Skeletons are resistant to piercing, bladed and cold-based attacks but are "
"vulnerable to impact, fire, and arcane attacks."
msgstr ""
"A csontvĂĄzak ellenĂĄllnak a szĂşrĂł, a vĂĄgĂł ĂŠs a hideg tĂĄmadĂĄsoknak, de "
"sebezhetĹek ĂźtĹ, tĹąz ĂŠs fĂśldĂśntĂşli tĂĄmadĂĄsokkal."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:144
msgid ""
"Units with the <i>Leadership</i> ability help lower-level adjacent units on "
"the same side fight better. You can move these units slowly along your "
"battle lines and give bonuses to large numbers of lower-level troops."
msgstr ""
"A <i>hadvezetĂŠs</i> kĂŠpessĂŠggel rendelkezĹ egysĂŠgek a kĂśzelĂźkben ĂĄllĂł, velĂźk "
"harcolĂł, alacsonyabb szintĹą egysĂŠgeket erĹsebbĂŠ teszik. Mozgasd megfontoltan "
"a hadvezetĹket a frontvonal mentĂŠn, hogy minĂŠl tĂśbb alacsonyabb szintĹą "
"egysĂŠg sebzĂŠsĂŠt erĹsĂ­tsĂŠk."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:148
msgid ""
"Try to avoid moving next to unoccupied villages. An enemy unit may move into "
"the village and attack you, while enjoying the defense and healing of the "
"village."
msgstr ""
"Gondold meg, mielĹtt egy Ăźres falu mellĂŠ lĂŠpsz! Egy ellensĂŠges egysĂŠg kĂśzben "
"belĂŠphet, ĂŠs megtĂĄmadhat, mikĂśzben ĂŠlvezi a falu nyĂşjtotta vĂŠdelmet ĂŠs "
"gyĂłgyulĂĄst."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:149
msgid "<i>â Great Mage Delfador, 516YW</i>"
msgstr "<i>â Delfador nagymĂĄgus, w.i.sz. 516.</i>"

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:152
msgid ""
"For any player, controlling villages is often key to winning a scenario. You "
"may use this knowledge to lure your opponents into a trap by leaving some "
"villages unoccupied, but keep in mind that an enemy unit becomes much harder "
"to dislodge from a village! Plan your movements accordingly."
msgstr ""
"A gyĹzelemhez minden jĂĄtĂŠkos szĂĄmĂĄra kulcsfontossĂĄgĂş, hogy elfoglalja a "
"falvakat. HasznĂĄld ezt a tudĂĄst ĂŠs csald csapdĂĄba ellenfeleidet nĂŠhĂĄny falu "
"Ăźresen hagyĂĄsĂĄval, de ne felejtsd el, hogy az ellensĂŠges egysĂŠget nehezebb "
"lesz kimozdĂ­tani a falubĂłl. Ennek megfelelĹen tervezd az egysĂŠgeid mozgĂĄsĂĄt."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:153
msgid "<i>â Kai Laudiss, 623YW</i>"
msgstr "<i>â Kai Laudiss, w.i.sz. 623.</i>"

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:156
msgid "Use lines of troops to screen your injured units while they recover."
msgstr ""
"ĂllĂ­tsd egysĂŠgeidet harcvonalba, hogy a mĂśgĂśttĂźk lĂŠvĹ egysĂŠgeket fedezzĂŠk, "
"amĂ­g felgyĂłgyulnak."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:157
msgid "<i>â Princess Liâsar, 515YW</i>"
msgstr "<i>â Liâsar hercegnĹ, w.i.sz. 515.</i>"

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:160
msgid ""
"If you move a unit, but donât attack or discover any additional information, "
"you can undo your move by pressing <b>u</b>."
msgstr ""
"Ha lĂŠpsz egy egysĂŠggel, de nem tĂĄmadsz, ĂŠs nem is tĂĄrsz fel Ăşj "
"kĂśrĂźlmĂŠnyeket, visszavonhatod a lĂŠpĂŠsed az <b>u</b> billentyĹą megnyomĂĄsĂĄval."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:164
msgid ""
"You can see how far enemy units can move by moving the mouse cursor over "
"them."
msgstr ""
"Ha az egĂŠrmutatĂłt egy egysĂŠg fĂślĂŠ viszed, lĂĄthatod milyen messzire tud lĂŠpni "
"egy kĂśr alatt."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:168
msgid ""
"Use healers to support your attacks â they will win you battles without "
"needing to attack anything themselves."
msgstr ""
"HasznĂĄlj gyĂłgyĂ­tĂł egysĂŠgeket tĂĄmadĂĄsaid segĂ­tĂŠsĂŠre â eldĂśnthetik a csatĂĄt "
"anĂŠlkĂźl, hogy bĂĄrkit is maguknak kellene megtĂĄmadniuk."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:169 data/tips.cfg:210
msgid "<i>â The Scroll of Chantal, 516YW</i>"
msgstr "<i>â Chantal tekercse, w.i.sz. 516.</i>"

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:172
msgid ""
"The <i>Slow</i> attack makes enemy units move slower and halves the damage "
"they do on all attacks until they end a turn."
msgstr ""
"A <i>lassĂ­tĂĄs</i> kĂŠpessĂŠge lelassĂ­tja az ellensĂŠget, ĂŠs megfelezi az ĂĄltala "
"kifejthetĹ sebzĂŠst is, amĂ­g az be nem fejezi sajĂĄt kĂśrĂŠt."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:176
msgid "<i>Arcane</i> attacks are very powerful against undead."
msgstr ""
"A <i>fĂśldĂśntĂşli</i> tĂĄmadĂĄsok kifejezetten hatĂŠkonyak ĂŠlĹholt egysĂŠgek ellen."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:177
msgid "<i>â Great Sage Dacyn, 626YW</i>"
msgstr "<i>â Dacyn, a Nagy BĂślcs, w.i.sz. 626.</i>"

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:180
msgid ""
"Units are healed when they advance a level. Used wisely, this can turn a "
"fight."
msgstr ""
"Amikor egy egysĂŠg szintet lĂŠp, akkor teljesen felgyĂłgyul. Ez, ha bĂślcsen "
"hasznĂĄlod, eldĂśntheti a csatĂĄt."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:184
msgid ""
"Charging units are best used against enemies they can kill with a single "
"blow."
msgstr ""
"A rohamegysĂŠgek azon ellensĂŠgekkel szemben a legjobbak, akiket elsĹ "
"nekifutĂĄsra meg tudnak Ăślni."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:188
msgid ""
"Once a unit reaches maximum level, further advancement provides a minor "
"bonus called an âAMLAâ â âAfter Maximum Level Advancement.â Some campaigns "
"let you choose between several AMLA options, but the only default AMLA is a "
"+3 bonus to maximum hitpoints. AMLAs are usually weaker than the normal "
"benefits of advancing a level, so it is generally wiser to advance your "
"lower-level units instead."
msgstr ""
"Amint egy egysĂŠg elĂŠri a maximĂĄlis szintet, a tovĂĄbbi elĹrelĂŠpĂŠs egy kisebb "
"bĂłnuszt biztosĂ­t, az \"LSzUSz\"-t (LegfelsĹbb Szint UtĂĄni SzintlĂŠpĂŠs). Egyes "
"hadjĂĄratok lehetĹvĂŠ teszik, hogy tĂśbb LSzUSz-opciĂł kĂśzĂźl vĂĄlasszunk, de az "
"egyetlen alapĂŠrtelmezett LSzUSz a +3 bĂłnusz a maximĂĄlis ĂŠleterĹponthoz. Az "
"LSzUSz-ok jutalmai ĂĄltalĂĄban gyengĂŠbbek, mint a normĂĄl szintlĂŠpĂŠsekĂŠ, ezĂŠrt "
"ĂĄltalĂĄban bĂślcsebb az alacsonyabb szintĹą egysĂŠgeket szintet lĂŠptetni."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:192
msgid ""
"To advance low-level units quickly, team them with a veteran and use the "
"veteran to damage a joint target heavily enough for the junior partner to "
"get in the killing blow."
msgstr ""
"Ahhoz, hogy alacsony szintĹą egysĂŠgeidet gyorsan szintet lĂŠptesd, csinĂĄlj "
"belĹlĂźk ĂŠs a veterĂĄn egysĂŠgekbĹl csapatot. A veterĂĄnokkal sebesĂ­tsd meg "
"annyira az ellenfelet, hogy az ifjonc egysĂŠgek megadhassĂĄk a gyilkos csapĂĄst."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:193
msgid "<i>â Queen Liâsar, 528YW</i>"
msgstr "<i>â Liâsar kirĂĄlynĹ, w.i.sz. 528.</i>"

#. [tip]
#. Whiteboard is another name for the Planning Mode
#: data/tips.cfg:197
msgid ""
"You cannot undo a move that uncovers hexes hidden by fog or shroud. Turn on "
"the <b>Delay Shroud Updates</b> option when you need to move units while "
"retaining the ability to undo, or use the new Whiteboard planning tool."
msgstr ""
"Azt a mozgĂĄst, amellyel kĂśd vagy kitakarĂĄs alĂłl fedtĂŠl fel terĂźletet, nem "
"tudod visszavonni. Kapcsold be az <b>EltakarĂĄs frissĂ­tĂŠsĂŠnek kĂŠsleltetĂŠse</"
"b> funkciĂłt, vagy hasznĂĄld az Ăşj lĂŠpĂŠstervezĹt, ha szeretnĂŠd Ăşgy mozgatni az "
"egysĂŠgeidet, hogy a visszavonĂĄs lehetĹsĂŠge megmaradjon."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:201
msgid ""
"If an enemy benefits more from a rare terrain type than you do, occupying "
"that terrain will deprive them of its benefits."
msgstr ""
"Ha egy ellensĂŠg nagyobb elĹnyhĂśz jut egy ritka tereptĂ­pusbĂłl, mint te, akkor "
"ezen terĂźletek elfoglalĂĄsĂĄval megfoszthatod ettĹl az elĹnytĹl."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:205
msgid ""
"Few units have good defenses in water; a line of attackers along the edge of "
"a river can inflict heavy casualties. Elves can use the edge of a forest in "
"a similar manner, and dwarves can do the same with mountains."
msgstr ""
"KevĂŠs egysĂŠgnek van jĂł vĂŠdekezĂŠse a vĂ­zben; a vĂ­z szĂŠlĂŠn felsorakozĂł tĂĄmadĂłk "
"komoly vesztesĂŠget okozhatnak az ellensĂŠgnek. A tĂźndĂŠk hasznĂĄlhatjĂĄk ezt a "
"mĂłdszert az erdĹ szĂŠlĂŠn, ĂŠs a tĂśrpĂśk is megtehetik ugyanezt a hegyeken."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:209
msgid ""
"The <i>Slow</i> ability is extremely powerful because it has such wide-"
"ranging effects. Enemy undead get half the normal benefit from their "
"<i>Drain</i> ability, the damage bonus from <i>Charge</i> or <i>Backstab</i> "
"is cancelled, and the <i>Berserk</i> ability is weakened. Fast foes struggle "
"to escape; slow enemies are almost immobilized, and your own units suffer "
"less retaliation damage, so itâs quicker to heal them."
msgstr ""
"A <i>lassĂ­tĂĄs</i> kĂŠpessĂŠge nagyon hatĂŠkony, mert szĂŠleskĂśrĹą hatĂĄsai vannak. "
"Az ellensĂŠges ĂŠlĹholtak a <i>megcsapolĂĄs</i> sorĂĄn csak a szokĂĄsos ĂŠletpont "
"felĂŠt kapjĂĄk meg, a <i>roham</i> ĂŠs a <i>hĂĄtbatĂĄmadĂĄs</i> elĹnyei teljesen "
"elvesznek, a <i>dĂźhĂśngĂŠs</i> is meggyengĂźl. A gyors ellensĂŠgek csak lassan "
"tudnak menekĂźlni, az eleve lassĂş ellensĂŠgek pedig szinte mozgĂĄskĂŠptelennĂŠ "
"vĂĄlnak. A sajĂĄt egysĂŠgeid a lassĂ­tĂĄstĂłl meggyengĂźlt ellenfelektĹl kevesebb "
"sĂŠrĂźlĂŠst szenvednek el, Ă­gy gyorsabban felgyĂłgyulnak."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:213
msgid ""
"Try to operate units with a small number of powerful attacks â such as Dark "
"Adepts, Horsemen, Orcish Grunts or Dwarvish Thunderers â in pairs or threes. "
"This gives you another try whenever your first devastating attack misses â "
"as inevitably happens from time to time."
msgstr ""
"HasznĂĄld a kis ĂźtĂŠsszĂĄmĂş, de nagy sebzĂŠsĹą egysĂŠgeidet â pĂŠldĂĄul az ĂĄrnyak "
"tanĂ­tvĂĄnya, a dzsidĂĄs, az ork kĂśzkatona, vagy a tĂśrp mennydĂśrgĹ â pĂĄrosĂĄval, "
"vagy hĂĄrmasĂĄval. Ăgy van mĂŠg egy lehetĹsĂŠged, ha az elsĹ pusztĂ­tĂł tĂĄmadĂĄsod "
"cĂŠlt tĂŠvesztett, ahogy az idĹrĹl idĹre elkerĂźlhetetlenĂźl megesik."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:217
msgid ""
"Units with three or more attacks â especially magical attacks â are ideal "
"for finishing off enemies with only a few hitpoints remaining. Be sure to "
"use leadership â or a strong or dextrous unit â whenever the extra point or "
"two of damage makes a one-hit kill possible."
msgstr ""
"A hĂĄrom vagy tĂśbb ĂźtĂŠssel rendelkezĹ egysĂŠgeid â kĂźlĂśnĂśsen, ha a tĂĄmadĂĄsuk "
"mĂĄgikus â kivĂĄlĂłan alkalmasak a kevĂŠs ĂŠletpontĂş ellenfelek vĂŠgsĹ "
"megsemmisĂ­tĂŠsĂŠre. Ne feledd el kihasznĂĄlni a hadvezetĂŠst, vagy egy erĹs vagy "
"ĂźgyeskezĹą egysĂŠged kĂŠpessĂŠgĂŠt, ha ĂŠpp csak ennyi sebzĂŠs hiĂĄnyzik hozzĂĄ, hogy "
"az ellenfeledet egyetlen csapĂĄssal megĂślhesd."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:221
msgid ""
"Think twice before dismissing any unit from your recall list, no matter how "
"little experience it has. Sometimes itâs worth paying a premium to know "
"exactly what traits a new arrival will have."
msgstr ""
"KĂŠtszer is gondold meg, mielĹtt elbocsĂĄtanĂĄl egy egysĂŠget a visszahĂ­vĂĄsi "
"listĂĄdrĂłl, akĂĄrmilyen kis tapasztalattal is rendelkezik. NĂŠha megĂŠri tĂśbb "
"aranyat fizetni egy egysĂŠgĂŠrt, ha pontosan tudjuk, hogy milyen "
"jellemvonĂĄsokkal ĂŠrkezik a csatatĂŠrre."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:225
msgid ""
"When a tough unit is heavily injured, send it to heal in a village several "
"turnsâ movement away from the fighting. Then it can recover in peace (at 10 "
"hitpoints per turn) without tying up front-line villages."
msgstr ""
"Amikor egy ĂŠrtĂŠkes egysĂŠg sĂşlyosan megsĂŠrĂźl, kĂźldd egy olyan faluba "
"gyĂłgyulni, amely tĂśbb kĂśrnyi tĂĄvolsĂĄgra van a csatĂĄtĂłl. Ott nyugodtan "
"ĂŠpĂźlhet fel (kĂśrĂśnkĂŠnt 10 ĂP-t), ĂŠs mĂŠg a frontvonalban lĂŠvĹ falvakat sem "
"foglalja le."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:226 data/tips.cfg:238
msgid "<i>â Lord Hamel of Knalga</i>"
msgstr "<i>â Hamel, Knalga ura</i>"

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:229
msgid ""
"Combining multiple special abilities can be deadly. While it may take some "
"work to combine, for example, <i>Leadership</i>, <i>Illuminates</i> and "
"<i>Charge</i> against a slowed opponent, the results can be impressive."
msgstr ""
"TĂśbb kĂźlĂśnleges kĂŠpessĂŠg ĂśsszpontosĂ­tott bevetĂŠse lehengerlĹ erejĹą. BĂĄr ez "
"sok fĂĄradtsĂĄggal jĂĄr, de igen lenyĹągĂśzĹ lehet, ha pĂŠldĂĄul <i>hadvezetĂŠst</"
"i>, <i>megvilĂĄgĂ­tĂĄst</i> ĂŠs <i>rohamot</i> vetĂźnk be egy lelassĂ­tott "
"ellenfĂŠllel szemben."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:233
msgid ""
"While finishing early gives a gold bonus, and reduces the opportunities for "
"enemies to kill your valuable troops, it also means you lose chances to earn "
"your units extra experience. When deciding whether or not to finish a "
"scenario early, weigh these factors against one another."
msgstr ""
"HabĂĄr a korai befejezĂŠsĂŠrt aranyjutalmat kapsz, ĂŠs ezzel az esĂŠlyĂŠt is "
"csĂśkkented, hogy az ellenfĂŠl megsemmisĂ­tse ĂŠrtĂŠkes egysĂŠgeidet, azt is "
"jelenti, hogy a csapataidat nem juttathatod tovĂĄbbi tapasztalathoz. "
"MĂŠrlegeld ezeket a tĂŠnyezĹket, mielĹtt eldĂśntenĂŠd, hogy tĂśrekedsz-e egy "
"kĂźldetĂŠs korai befejezĂŠsĂŠre."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:237
msgid ""
"If your forces have weak defenses everywhere on the map, occupy the areas "
"where your enemies can only attack you by sharing the same disadvantages. "
"Avoid places where your defenses are poor and your enemyâs are merely "
"average. Plan for heavy losses, and take firm control of any hex where the "
"land does favor you."
msgstr ""
"Ha olyan a tĂŠrkĂŠp, hogy az egysĂŠgeid mindenhol kedvezĹtlen terepen "
"harcolnak, foglald el azokat a pontokat, ahol az ellenfeled is hozzĂĄd "
"hasonlĂłan hĂĄtrĂĄnyban van. KerĂźld el azokat a helyeket, ahol gyenge a "
"vĂŠdelmed, mĂ­g az ellenfeledĂŠ ĂĄtlagos. SzĂĄmĂ­ts sĂşlyos vesztesĂŠgekre, ĂŠs "
"rendĂźletlenĂźl Ĺrizd azokat a mezĹket, ahol kedvezĹ szĂĄmodra a terep."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:241
msgid ""
"The recruitment cost of some units may exceed the usual recall expenditure "
"of 20 gold. In a campaign, always check if recalling a unit of the same type "
"may be cheaper."
msgstr ""
"NĂŠmely egysĂŠg toborzĂĄsi kĂśltsĂŠge meghaladhatja a 20 aranyba kerĂźlĹ "
"visszahĂ­vĂĄst. HadjĂĄratok sorĂĄn ĂŠrdemes ellenĹrizni, hogy az adott tĂ­pusĂş "
"egysĂŠg visszahĂ­vĂĄsa olcsĂłbb-e."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:245
msgid ""
"You must accept some losses in battle. It is not uncommon for beginners to "
"lose sight of victory as they attempt to keep every unit alive."
msgstr ""
"El kell fogadnod valamekkora vesztesĂŠget a csatĂĄban. Nem ritka, hogy a "
"kezdĹk szem elĹl tĂŠvesztik a gyĹzelmet, amikor megprĂłbĂĄlnak ĂŠletben tartani "
"minden egysĂŠget."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:246
msgid "<i>â Queen Asheviere, 503YW</i>"
msgstr "<i>â Asheviere kirĂĄlynĹ, w.i.sz. 503.</i>"

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:249
msgid "Using lower-level units can be very cost-effective."
msgstr ""
"Az alacsonyabb szintĹą egysĂŠgek hasznĂĄlata nagyon kĂśltsĂŠghatĂŠkony lehet."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:253
msgid ""
"Some higher-level units have inimitable abilities such as <i>Leadership</i>, "
"<i>Cures</i>, or <i>Nightstalk</i>. Obtaining those units early can make a "
"big difference in a campaign."
msgstr ""
"NĂŠhĂĄny magasabb szintĹą egysĂŠg utĂĄnozhatatlan kĂŠpessĂŠgekkel rendelkezik, mint "
"pĂŠldĂĄul a <i>VezetĂŠs</i>, a <i>GyĂłgyĂ­tĂĄs</i> vagy az <i>Ăjjeli lopakodĂĄs</"
"i>. Ezeknek az egysĂŠgeknek a korai megszerzĂŠse nagy elĹnyt jelenthet egy "
"hadjĂĄratban."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:254
msgid "<i>â Sir Gerrick of Westin, 607YW</i>"
msgstr "<i>â Sir Gerrick of Westin, W.i.sz. 607</i>"

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:257
msgid ""
"The cleansing waters of an oasis will heal the injured. The fiery ichor of "
"the underworld hinders the flightless, while offering illumination in "
"darkness to those that may fly above it."
msgstr ""
"Az oĂĄzis tisztĂ­tĂł vize meggyĂłgyĂ­tja a sebesĂźlteket. Az alvilĂĄg tĂźzes "
"lĂĄvatĂłcsĂĄi akadĂĄlyozzĂĄk a rĂśpkĂŠpteleneket, mikĂśzben a sĂśtĂŠtsĂŠgben "
"megvilĂĄgĂ­tĂĄst kĂ­nĂĄlnak a fĂślĂśttĂźk repĂźlĹ lĂŠnyeknek."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:258
msgid "<i>â Dominant Gorlack, 3YW</i>"
msgstr "<i>â Gorlack uralkodĂł, W.i.sz. 3</i>"

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:261
msgid ""
"If a unit is positioned next to healers from two allied sides, the unit will "
"be healed on both sidesâ turns. This way, a unit can be healed faster than "
"otherwise possible."
msgstr ""
"Ha egy egysĂŠg kĂŠt szĂśvetsĂŠges oldal gyĂłgyĂ­tĂłi mellett helyezkedik el, akkor "
"az egysĂŠg mindkĂŠt fĂŠl kĂśrĂŠben gyĂłgyul. Ăgy az egysĂŠg gyorsabban gyĂłgyĂ­thatĂł, "
"mint egyĂŠbkĂŠnt lehetsĂŠges lenne."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:262
msgid "<i>â Lord Tallin of Knalga, 538 YW</i>"
msgstr "<i>â Lord Tallin of Knalga, W.i.sz. 538</i>"

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:265
msgid ""
"Holding down <b>shift</b> will make the animations for moving and fighting "
"quicker. The <i>acceleration factor</i> can be set, and turned on by "
"default, in the <i>Preferences</i> menuâs <i>General</i> tab."
msgstr ""
"A <b>shift</b> lenyomva tartĂĄsa gyorsabbĂĄ teszi a mozgĂĄs ĂŠs a harc "
"animĂĄciĂłit. A <i>gyorsulĂĄsi tĂŠnyezĹ</i> a <i>BeĂĄllĂ­tĂĄsok</i> menĂź "
"<i>ĂltalĂĄnos</i> lapjĂĄn ĂĄllĂ­thatĂł ĂŠs kapcsolhatĂł be."

#. [tip]
#. Translate "Change difficulty" and "Load Game" as in wesnoth-lib textdomain
#: data/tips.cfg:270
msgid ""
"Did you know that you can change the difficulty level during a campaign? "
"Select the <i>Change difficulty</i> option at the bottom of the <i>Load "
"Game</i> screen when loading start-of-scenario save files."
msgstr ""
"Tudtad, hogy a kampĂĄny sorĂĄn megvĂĄltoztathatod a nehĂŠzsĂŠgi szintet? VĂĄlassza "
"a <i>NehĂŠzsĂŠg mĂłdosĂ­tĂĄsa</i> opciĂłt a <i>JĂĄtĂŠk betĂśltĂŠse</i> kĂŠpernyĹ aljĂĄn "
"a mentett kĂźldetĂŠsek betĂśltĂŠsekor."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:275
msgid ""
"<i>Feral</i> units, such as Bats and wild animals, will avoid villages. Even "
"if they occupy a village hex, they do not gain any defensive benefits from "
"the village, although they will still be healed."
msgstr ""
"A <i>kĂłbor</i> egysĂŠgek â pĂŠldĂĄul denevĂŠrek, vadĂĄllatok â elkerĂźlik a "
"falvakat. MĂŠg ha el is foglalnak egy falut, nem nyĂşjt jobb vĂŠdelmet "
"szĂĄmukra, habĂĄr a tĂśbbi egysĂŠghez hasonlĂłan gyĂłgyulnak."

#. [tip]
#: data/tips.cfg:281
msgid ""
"Nearly every hotkey can be customized in the <b>Preferences</b> > "
"<b>Hotkeys</b> tab. Rebinding frequently used actions (Undo, Show Enemy "
"Moves, End Turn, Recruit/Recall) to comfortable keys can noticeably speed up "
"your turns and improve your quality of life."
msgstr ""
"Szinte minden gyorsbillentyĹą testreszabhatĂł a <b>BeĂĄllĂ­tĂĄsok</b> > "
"<b>GyorsbillentyĹąk</b> lapon. A gyakran hasznĂĄlt mĹąveletek (VisszavonĂĄs, "
"EllensĂŠges mozgĂĄs megjelenĂ­tĂŠse, KĂśr befejezĂŠse, ToborzĂĄs/VisszahĂ­vĂĄs) a "
"jĂĄtĂŠkos szĂĄmĂĄra kĂŠnyelmes billentyĹąkre valĂł ĂĄtdefiniĂĄlĂĄsa ĂŠrezhetĹen "
"felgyorsĂ­thatja a kĂśreit ĂŠs javĂ­tja a komfortjĂĄt."

