#: src/savegame.cpp:132
msgid ""
"This save is from a different version of the game ($version_number|), and "
"might not work with this version.\n"
"\n"
"<b>Warning:</b> saves in the middle of campaigns are especially likely to "
"fail, and you should either use the old version or restart the campaign. "
"Even when a saved game seems to load successfully, subtler aspects like "
"gameplay balance and story progression could be impacted. The difficulty, "
"the challenge, the <i>fun</i> may be missing.\n"
"\n"
"For example, the campaign may have been rebalanced with fewer enemies in the "
"early scenarios, but expecting your recall list to have correspondingly less "
"experience in the late scenarios.\n"
"\n"
"Do you wish to continue?"
msgstr ""
"Ez a mentĂŠs a jĂĄtĂŠk egy mĂĄsik verziĂłjĂĄbĂłl szĂĄrmazik ($version_number|), ĂŠs "
"elĹfordulhat, hogy nem mĹąkĂśdik ezzel a verziĂłval.\n"
"\n"
"<b>FigyelmeztetĂŠs:</b> a hadjĂĄratok kĂśzben tĂśrtĂŠnĹ mentĂŠsek kĂźlĂśnĂśsen "
"valĂłszĂ­nĹą, hogy sikertelenek lesznek, ezĂŠrt vagy a rĂŠgi verziĂłt kell "
"hasznĂĄlnia, vagy Ăşjra kell indĂ­tania a hadjĂĄratot. MĂŠg ha Ăşgy is tĹąnik, hogy "
"egy mentett jĂĄtĂŠk sikeresen betĂśltĹdĂśtt, hatĂĄssal lehet a jĂĄtĂŠkmenet olyan "
"finomabb aspektusaira, mint a jĂĄtĂŠkmenet egyensĂşlya, vagy a tĂśrtĂŠnet "
"elĹrehaladĂĄsa. A nehĂŠzsĂŠg, a kihĂ­vĂĄs, a <i>szĂłrakozĂĄs</i> hiĂĄnyozhat.\n"
"\n"
"PĂŠldĂĄul lehet, hogy a hadjĂĄrat ĂĄthangolĂłdik kevesebb ellensĂŠggel a hadjĂĄrat "
"elsĹ kĂźldetĂŠseiben, de az egysĂŠg visszahĂ­vĂĄsi listĂĄdon lĂŠvĹ egysĂŠgek kevĂŠsbĂŠ "
"tudnak fejlĹdni a kĂŠsĹbbi kĂźldetĂŠsekben.\n"
"\n"
"SzeretnĂŠ folytatni?"

